{"tid":2239842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BTS稱永記朝鮮戰爭韓美共同經歷　內地網民轟辱華：「滾出中國」","createTime":"2020-10-12T09:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T09:35:45.000Z","uid":367354,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9da20903006aac08820ce39019adee814fb9ba","tid":2239842,"uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"Source:HK01<br />\n<br />\n10月11日，韓國男子組合防彈少年團（BTS）對韓美關係做出貢獻獲得范佛里特獎（James A. Van Fleet Award）。其在發表感言時表示，會銘記朝鮮戰爭中，美國和韓國共同經歷的苦難歷史。<br />\n<br />\n相關發言被中國網民轉發至微博等內地社交平台，許多內地網民指BTS發言不當，侮辱了朝鮮戰爭中的中國人民志願軍，相關消息更登上微博熱搜。有BTS粉絲稱「國家面前無偶像，希望大家牢記」，還有網民表示，防彈少年團「可以滾出中國市場了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fe7921b6718f4933bfb3dc5926de3f01b11bcb","tid":2239842,"uid":42762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"國家面前無偶像，希望大家牢記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防彈少年團「可以滾出中國市場了」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTS出新歌<br />\n<br />\n支麻人：真香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f963e44ed681db1964decf5fd1cb5742bfc5fe0c","tid":2239842,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"雖然文在寅奶共，不過韓國人好憎中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cmmedia.com.tw/file/41879/1602054630_100098_%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F(1).png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmmedia.com.tw%2Ffile%2F41879%2F1602054630_100098_%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%25BC%258F%281%29.png&h=33466c0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca1c638622c76179708dbdd1fa24eae6800e1d2","tid":2239842,"uid":323720,"